704170f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ferris Street - Dikeman Street
704170f-a.text:
Ferris Street (rear of "Cook Electrically" building, a Brooklyn
Edison Company building) between Dikeman (left) and Coffey Streets
(right). lIn the foreground is the Buttermilk Channel.
August 6, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
